    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到Pending状态内部需要关联库存系统做审核，那AwaitingModeration这个中间状态是放在Pending内部作为子状态，还是和Pending并列？另外删除操作是在哪些状态下都能执行吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "AwaitingModeration",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Deleted"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "AwaitingModeration放在Pending内部作为子状态，它和库存系统之间双向流转。删除操作需要在Pending、Approved、Rejected三个状态下都能触发，最终流转到客户忠诚度模块归档。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "AwaitingModeration",
        "Retail_Inventory",
        "Deleted",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主干：从订单管理创建评论进入Pending，Pending内部包含AwaitingModeration与库存系统的检查循环。然后Pending可以Approve到Approved状态，或者Reject到Rejected状态。三个主状态都能Delete到Deleted，最终指向客户忠诚度模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Pending",
        "AwaitingModeration",
        "Approved",
        "Rejected",
        "Deleted",
